{
  "id": "6a08feaf644fd248f4037a3b",
  "title": "#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk148: 大阪・兵庫旅行 with 5歳の娘",
  "created": 1778974385,
  "updated": 1779579435,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a08feaf644fd248f4037a3b",
      "text": "#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk148: 大阪・兵庫旅行 with 5歳の娘",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778974385,
      "updated": 1778974385
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09022d0000000000696713",
      "text": "[https://open.spotify.com/episode/5oiftbjifDrmoWpSgKUWwW]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975277,
      "updated": 1778975281
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09022e0000000000696714",
      "text": "\t[Google Formsで感想を送る https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1fC9gUB6PC3uJidZAJ8pgD1qLiMdvIgZOenrTwcOqpnw/]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975278,
      "updated": 1778975309
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09024c0000000000696715",
      "text": " [Discordサーバー「inajob川」に参加する https://discord.gg/vHu4CXuMPq]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975309,
      "updated": 1778975309
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09024c0000000000696716",
      "text": " \t[参加する前に様子を見る https://inajob.github.io/inajob-river-peeker/]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975309,
      "updated": 1778975309
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09024c0000000000696717",
      "text": "\t[LISTENでの文字起こし https://listen.style/p/inajob/nj9uajvs]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975309,
      "updated": 1778976718
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0907d40000000000adeef2",
      "text": "\t\t> このエピソードでは、ポッドキャストホストのいなじょぶさんが、5歳の娘さんと共に大阪・兵庫を訪れたゴールデンウィーク旅行について語っています。大阪城や道頓堀での観光、神戸に住む弟さん一家との交流、そして実家のある兵庫県田島でのタケノコ掘りや竹田城、生野銀山訪問など、多岐にわたる体験が語られました。特に、生野銀山で出会った「銀山ボーイズ」というご当地アイドルに娘さんが夢中になったエピソードや、特急列車のフリースペースでの交流など、子供連れならではの楽しみ方が紹介されています。",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778976725,
      "updated": 1778976726
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08feb1000000000069670e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778974385,
      "updated": 1779488005
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d13f0000000000749cf5",
      "text": "\t健康",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487039,
      "updated": 1779487042
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d1410000000000749cf6",
      "text": "\t\t[イネ花粉]の影響受ける",
      "userId": "58d101391094b20011d8c2f4",
      "created": 1779487042,
      "updated": 1779579435
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d1800000000000749cf9",
      "text": "\t\t\t目がおかしい、目薬で対応",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487104,
      "updated": 1779487110
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d1450000000000749cf7",
      "text": "\t\t花粉レーダーのWebサイトではスギ・ヒノキの事しか教えてくれない問題",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487045,
      "updated": 1779487077
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d1650000000000749cf8",
      "text": "\t\t\tイネは飛散範囲が狭くて地図に表すのが難しいのかな？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487077,
      "updated": 1779487098
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d18f0000000000749cfa",
      "text": "\tゴールデンウィークの旅行の話",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487119,
      "updated": 1779487127
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d1970000000000749cfb",
      "text": "\t\t4月24日の午後から前入りするスタイル",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487127,
      "updated": 1779487143
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d1a70000000000749cfc",
      "text": "\t\t2日残して帰宅してきて、のんびり過ごすことで平日をスムーズに迎えられるようにした",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487143,
      "updated": 1779487165
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2210000000000749d03",
      "text": "\t新大阪に宿をとる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487265,
      "updated": 1779487294
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2420000000000749d06",
      "text": "\t\t551の肉まん・ちまき",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487299,
      "updated": 1779487299
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2420000000000749d07",
      "text": "\t\tホテルに海外の人が多い",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487299,
      "updated": 1779487299
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2420000000000749d08",
      "text": "\t\t\tランドリーの使い方を他の客から英語で教えてもらう体験（なぜ？）",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487299,
      "updated": 1779487299
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2380000000000749d05",
      "text": "\t弟家族に会いに行く",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487288,
      "updated": 1779487299
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2260000000000749d04",
      "text": "\t\t赤ちゃんとご対面",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487270,
      "updated": 1779487273
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08feb40000000000696710",
      "text": "\t大阪観光",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778974388,
      "updated": 1778975339
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d1e10000000000749d00",
      "text": "\t\t[大阪うまいもんの歌]を5歳の娘が歌っていたので歌に出てくるものを見に行こうか、という目論見",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487201,
      "updated": 1779487297
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09028a000000000069671e",
      "text": "\t\t大阪城",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975370,
      "updated": 1778975372
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d25d0000000000749d0b",
      "text": "\t\t\t天守閣まで登る",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487325,
      "updated": 1779487329
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2610000000000749d0c",
      "text": "\t\t\t大道芸を見る",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487329,
      "updated": 1779487331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2630000000000749d0d",
      "text": "\t\t\t剣道の試合を見る",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487331,
      "updated": 1779487336
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09028c000000000069671f",
      "text": "\t\t道頓堀",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975372,
      "updated": 1778975377
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2500000000000749d09",
      "text": "\t\t\tたこ焼き",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487313,
      "updated": 1779487318
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2550000000000749d0a",
      "text": "\t\t\tお好み焼き",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487318,
      "updated": 1779487320
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09026b0000000000696719",
      "text": "\t但馬観光",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975339,
      "updated": 1778975341
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d1c30000000000749cfe",
      "text": "\t\t但馬",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487171,
      "updated": 1779487174
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2740000000000749d0e",
      "text": "\t\t\t兵庫県の一地域",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487348,
      "updated": 1779487353
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2a90000000000749d0f",
      "text": "\t\t細かい話",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487401,
      "updated": 1779487405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2c30000000000749d12",
      "text": "\t\t\t畑のダンゴムシ（マルムシ）取り",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487427,
      "updated": 1779487459
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2ac0000000000749d10",
      "text": "\t\t\t知育菓子",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487405,
      "updated": 1779487412
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2b40000000000749d11",
      "text": "\t\t\t本当は怖い日本昔話",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487412,
      "updated": 1779487419
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2cc0000000000749d13",
      "text": "\t\t\t図書館",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487436,
      "updated": 1779487437
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2cf0000000000749d14",
      "text": "\t\t\t5歳の娘と掃除",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487439,
      "updated": 1779487446
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d2eb0000000000749d15",
      "text": "\t\t\t手持ち花火",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487467,
      "updated": 1779487469
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d30f0000000000749d16",
      "text": "\t\t\tUNOは毎晩遊んだ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487503,
      "updated": 1779487509
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d3170000000000749d17",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t「ウノ！」というのはみんなで教え合うローカルルール",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487512,
      "updated": 1779487522
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d32b0000000000749d18",
      "text": "\t\t\t父親のパソコンを買う",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487531,
      "updated": 1779487536
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d3300000000000749d19",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tその間5歳の娘は光ナビゲーションキーボードで遊ぶ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487537,
      "updated": 1779487547
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d33a0000000000749d1a",
      "text": "\t\t\t5歳の娘が種まきを体験",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487547,
      "updated": 1779487561
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d3490000000000749d1b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t意外と面白かったらしい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487561,
      "updated": 1779487565
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d35f0000000000749d1c",
      "text": "\t\t\tジグソーパズル",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487583,
      "updated": 1779487585
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d3910000000000749d1f",
      "text": "\t\t\t海鮮せんべいの試食",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487633,
      "updated": 1779487647
    },
    {
      "id": "6a090285000000000069671d",
      "text": "\t\tタケノコ掘り",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975367,
      "updated": 1778975369
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09026d000000000069671a",
      "text": "\t\t[竹田城]跡",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975341,
      "updated": 1778975434
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d37e0000000000749d1d",
      "text": "\t\t\t日本のマチュピチュなどと呼ばれているのだとか",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487614,
      "updated": 1779487622
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d3860000000000749d1e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t雲海が出るといい感じらしい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487622,
      "updated": 1779487629
    },
    {
      "id": "6a090276000000000069671b",
      "text": "\t\t[生野銀山]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975350,
      "updated": 1778975437
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d3c50000000000749d21",
      "text": "\t\t\t雨でもなんとか見て回れた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487685,
      "updated": 1779487698
    },
    {
      "id": "6a090279000000000069671c",
      "text": "\t\t\t[GINZAN BOYZ]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975353,
      "updated": 1778975362
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d3ad0000000000749d20",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t後に親子で歌を覚えて歌えるようになった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487661,
      "updated": 1779487671
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4140000000000749d22",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t歌と観光って相性がよさそう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487765,
      "updated": 1779487772
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d41c0000000000749d23",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t[那須塩原]の時も[juneboku]さんの作った歌を口ずさんでいたなぁ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487772,
      "updated": 1779487799
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4390000000000749d24",
      "text": "\t\t特急列車",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487802,
      "updated": 1779487805
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d43c0000000000749d25",
      "text": "\t\t\tフリースペース付きで良かった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487805,
      "updated": 1779487811
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4430000000000749d26",
      "text": "\t\t\t連結作業を見ることが出来た",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487812,
      "updated": 1779487817
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4480000000000749d27",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tここに鉄道好きの子供が集まってきていて、その後仲良くなってよかった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487817,
      "updated": 1779487849
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4590000000000749d28",
      "text": "\t\t\t一方新幹線はとても退屈だった・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487833,
      "updated": 1779487842
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0902650000000000696718",
      "text": "\tこういうマイナーな旅先の話はもっと聞きたい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778975333,
      "updated": 1779487919
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4af0000000000749d2a",
      "text": "\t\t実家に帰るなどがその典型だと思うが、ローカルな名所みたいなものを教えてほしい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487920,
      "updated": 1779487940
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4ce0000000000749d2b",
      "text": "\t\tまずは自分から話してみる、という回のつもり",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487950,
      "updated": 1779487963
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4db0000000000749d2c",
      "text": "\t兵庫に帰るのは毎年のイベントになりそうなので、周辺の観光を開拓していきたい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487963,
      "updated": 1779487985
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4f10000000000749d2d",
      "text": "\t\t岡山・淡路島・香川・京都・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487985,
      "updated": 1779487997
    },
    {
      "id": "6a10d4990000000000749d29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1779487898,
      "updated": 1779487898
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08febc0000000000696712",
      "text": "\t前回",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778974397,
      "updated": 1778974398
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08feb50000000000696711",
      "text": "\t\t[#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk147:Microsoft Officeによるベンダーロックインと実家・スマートEX・シール交換]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778974389,
      "updated": 1778974399
    },
    {
      "id": "6a08feb1000000000069670f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1778974385,
      "updated": 1778974385
    }
  ]
}